    <p>Teams must use the official Attributions form. This form clearly delineates the work conducted by your team members and the support received from others. Carefully review the instructions and requirements of this deliverable on the <a href="https://competition.igem.org/deliverables/project-attribution">Project Attribution page</a>. Please note:</p>
